description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Core Pilates' from the channel Christie Wang.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The The Masterclass Workout vibe means Technique-driven, focused, skill-building. This is especially good for Those who love precision and mastery in movement..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Strengthen your core with Christie and James during this quick workout from Lucerne, Switzerland. ...
